# GitHub Packages registry for @hemut2025/* private packages.
#
# Auth comes from the NPM_TOKEN environment variable (npm expands ${NPM_TOKEN}
# at install time) — NO secret is stored in this file, so it is safe to commit.
#   • Local dev:  export NPM_TOKEN=<your GitHub PAT with read:packages>
#   • Vercel/CI:  set NPM_TOKEN in the project's Environment Variables
# Create/rotate the PAT at https://github.com/settings/tokens.
@hemut2025:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
